{"tid":2178721,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK 《Ice Cream》MV面世4小時 點擊率衝破2千萬大關","createTime":"2020-08-28T14:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T11:48:32.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ee1d77140baf28f1555bbfcc02917390ac381da0","tid":2178721,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T14:31:40.000Z","msg":"BLACKPINK 顆拍修身成功的美國小天后Selena Gomez的新歌《Ice Cream》 MV在今午面世，播出後4小時點擊率已衝破2千萬大關，一日破億不是夢。BLACKPINK一改以往有型又霸氣的Style，着好Colourful的短裙小背心大玩甜美少女風，眾人不斷拎住雪糕跳舞，齊齊大show苗條身材，夏日氣氛非常濃厚。<br />\n<br />\nMV中，BACKPINK與Selena Gomez雖沒有同場演出，但兩者的造型跟風格都能完美配合，豪無違和感。曲風輕快的《ICE CREAM》幾乎全曲以英文演唱，但仍能保留BLACKPINK的個人特色，各人的Solo鏡頭各有千秋，MV中不論場景，造型，色調都繽紛多變，誠意十足。BLACKPINK與Selena Gomez都是少女們的潮流icon，MV中她們的造型服飾都大膽誇張，鮮艷奪目，相信又會引起無數少女模仿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vRXZj0DzXIA&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvRXZj0DzXIA%26feature%3Demb_title&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyEYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=e3f9e280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vRXZj0DzXIA&amp;feature=emb_title</a>"},{"pid":"7f3b58265772cdf7d7d615d01869b7d80a8b86e7","tid":2178721,"uid":165368,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T14:56:07.000Z","msg":"先唔講selena有fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4小時前嘅view就咪鬼貼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fe6cd47a576cc723a9c090523ee3d7322bb921","tid":2178721,"uid":161650,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"Jisoo全首歌得一句歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a8f6310d6fdc4d4faaa58ee2451a1af297f521","tid":2178721,"uid":337986,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T18:30:09.000Z","msg":"Rose由出道到而家都好瘦 <br />\n想知佢一日三餐食乜"},{"pid":"f271382f423971822fe68fbb033486d58f2fda7a","tid":2178721,